description: Hi i am youssef from Morocco , i was using ubuntu 16.04 LTS . now i installe budgie remix 16.10 , soo i am new , can you give me same advance .
comments.comment: Hi - I think you are asking for some advice how to use budgie-desktop?  Run budgie-welcome from the menu and choose the Getting Started button.  That will run through with you the basics of budgie-desktop and how to use.  Have fun!
